        public void onTeamChangeEvent(TeamChangeEvent event)
        Method that receives a TeamChangeEvent and sorts through it placing the players in oder by playerId. When a player is found it matches the player and the team number i in a Pair. When all players are sorted it sets the value in the mutableLiveData.
        Parameters:
        event - - event containing Teams which in turn hold players.
